(1031, 'If (2a + 3b)/(5a - 3b) = 23/5 , then the value of ba is ?', 'A) 5', 'B) 4', 'C) 20', 'D) 28', 'c', 'Given (2a + 3b)/(5a - 3b) = 23/5 => 10a + 15b = 115a - 69b=> 105a = 84b => 5a = 4b a/b = 4/5 => a=4 & b=5=> bxa = 5x4 = 20.', 0),
