(3034, 'If n is natural number , then?6n2+6n?is always divisible by :', 'A) 6 only', 'B) 6 and 12  both', 'C) 12 only', 'D) by 18 only', 'b', '6n2+6n=6nn+1,?which is always divisible by 6 and 12 both, since n(n+1) is always even.', 0),
