(7846, 'Which Country?hosted the 10th edition of BRICS Summit 2018?', 'A) Brazil', 'B) South Africa', 'C) India', 'D) Russia', 'b', 'South Africa hosted?the 10th edition of BRICS Summit 2018 in Johannesburg on July 25.?', 2),
